projectData.title: Travel App
projectData.description: React native and Go based mobile application for helping travelers plan vacations by offering a platform to organize their itinerary and receive ai recommendations using GPT-3.5. Users can organize multiple vacation dates, desired restaurants, interesting activities, and use helpful suggestions to plan their trip.

projectData.title: Gemini Dev AI
projectData.description: A web application that uses GPT-3.5 to help developers plan, elaborate on and organize their projects. This tool lets users enter their ideas for potential titles, project descriptions, features, etc. to consolidate their research, and then also provides ai-based assistance building upon and expanding their ideas.

projectData.title: Ixie AI
projectData.description: A web application that uses GPT-3.5 to help developers analyze and improve code quality. Users are able to upload a code sample with a description and receive feedback from other developers as well as generated feedback from GPT.

projectData.title: Wander Wise API
projectData.description: RESTful API service built on node.js for providing backend services to the Wander Wise Frontend application. This API provides endpoints for user authentication, itinerary creation, and itinerary recommendations.
